{"body_text": "ESLint-plugin-mozilla has had a lot of updates recently, especially for being used outside of mozilla-central.\nAs a result it handles globals and other items a lot better than it used to, and this can then be used to clean up Normandy's code.\nWe also have a mozilla/recommended configuration (as well as a couple of others), so I've removed duplicate rules for those.\nTests may fail until 1.0.1 of the normandy configuration is released.", "labels": [], "number": 772, "assignee": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/Standard8", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/520844?v=4", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/received_events", "gravatar_id": "", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "Standard8", "type": "User", "id": 520844, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Standard8/followers"}, "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/normandy", "closed_at": "2017-05-23T18:15:49Z", "body_html": "<p>ESLint-plugin-mozilla has had a lot of updates recently, especially for being used outside of mozilla-central.</p>\n<p>As a result it handles globals and other items a lot better than it used to, and this can then be used to clean up Normandy's code.</p>\n<p>We also have a mozilla/recommended configuration (as well as a couple of others), so I've removed duplicate rules for those.</p>\n<p>Tests may fail until 1.0.1 of the normandy configuration is released.<